{"tid":1000762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"免費媒體難生存 美知名網媒BuzzFeed等大裁員","createTime":"2019-01-29T15:44:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T03:23:04.000Z","uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f7355e943aeabb26aa62ef6e2e441cf4a0af2e99","tid":1000762,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T15:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2019/01/29/phpocUTf7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F01%2F29%2FphpocUTf7.jpg&h=f5110333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國兩大網路媒體《赫芬頓郵報》（HuffPost）和BuzzFeed分別在上週和本週宣佈裁員。圖為BuzzFeed辦公室。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕美國兩大網路媒體《赫芬頓郵報》（HuffPost）和BuzzFeed分別在上週和本週宣佈裁員，《赫芬頓郵報》母公司稱其媒體部門將削減7％的員工人數，約800人，BuzzFeed則稱將削減15%的員工，約達250人。Buzzfeed執行長表示，其收入增長程度，在長期上不足以支持該媒體成功。<br />\n<br />\n《衛報》報導，美國網路媒體《赫芬頓郵報》母公司Verizon，上週稱其包括HuffPost、雅虎等在內的媒體部門，將削減7％的員工，約達800人，《赫芬頓郵報》約有10％的記者離開編輯人員，共約20人。<br />\n<br />\n而全球約有1100名員工的BuzzFeed，本週一稱將裁員15％，約250人。BuzzFeed創始人兼職行長Jonah Peretti在給員工的內部信稱，該公司的收入增長不足以長期支持其成功，而透過降低成本，「我們可以茁壯成長，控制自己的命運，且無需再次籌集資金」。<br />\n<br />\n其他網路媒體如時尚媒體Refinery29、新聞媒體Vox、影音媒體Group Nine Media雖然皆在網路影片領域取得進展，但它們在過去18個月裡都在裁員。<br />\n<br />\n美國傳媒教育中心Poynter Institute媒體商業分析師Rick Edmonds表示，網路媒體成立的出發點，幾乎是為了集合一大群觀眾，然後按大量觀眾數字出售廣告，但「Goolge和臉書的觀眾已經有更多成長，他們也更擅長收集訊息，並針對群體投放資訊」。據eMarketer預測，Google和臉書在2018年的廣告收入，約佔其總收入的57.7％，比2011年的45.5％大幅增長。<br />\n<br />\n波士頓大學（Boston University） 溝通管理學院（College of Communication）新聞學教授Christopher Daly指出，任何依賴廣告的新聞媒體都很難生存，並認為新聞業唯一真正可靠的資金來源是觀眾，「他們比廣告商、富有的顧客、政黨或任何其他資金來源更可靠」。<br />\n<br />\nBuzzFeed則已在去年11月推出每月5美元的訂閱計劃，其主站仍維持免費。但Edmonds認為，當一個媒體讓人們習慣於長期免費使用，便很難向付費媒體轉型。<br />\n<a href=\"http://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2687026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2687026&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMBYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=ffa03004\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2687026&h=2f0d8407\" target=\"_blank\">http://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2687026</a>"},{"pid":"f83a29cb1ec02c5d305bada75830d0165a0cab2c","tid":1000762,"uid":34410,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T15:46:19.000Z","msg":"好似話好多左膠女權俾人炒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae43e363dc3e44f54d1a4014008849121a0d956","tid":1000762,"uid":53687,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T15:49:25.000Z","msg":"抵啦，最憎 content farm"},{"pid":"f4d1153b10874000b9bc47d20cd7872b652417a7","tid":1000762,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T15:54:25.000Z","msg":"越來越垃圾唔好賴免費媒體"},{"pid":"0f5d4add45a92814e63642dd835eb9173f76324c","tid":1000762,"uid":34410,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RAz579w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRAz579w.jpg&h=caa80a4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3679c8a47e3f67171146c8d963eff18abf4b95d","tid":1000762,"uid":36432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:21:54.000Z","msg":"邊揀個會俾錢睇Buzzfeed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e72c074e1e6e5f45f702e0d99ecba5383bcfac9d","tid":1000762,"uid":26332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:25:58.000Z","msg":"You are FAKE NEWS！"},{"pid":"269dbafce25b1fe4d2f9dcd91f7c6b6be3eca1bd","tid":1000762,"uid":81598,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:30:03.000Z","msg":"buzzfeed根本垃撚圾，只係比班SJW同feminist捽碟既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c2cb0190a80bbe2dfa6bb34ee860db0c2ea1d5","tid":1000762,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-